Package Model.Car

Class CarDatabase

java.lang.Object
Model.Car.CarDatabase
All Implemented Interfaces:
interfaces.ModelDatabase
public class CarDatabase extends Object implements interfaces.ModelDatabase
CarDatabase model class that represents a database that stores Car objects. There is a local database for demonstration purposes and an AWS database.
